igence''\n| Herself\n| Television documentary film; also executive producer\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[My Boy Jack (film)|My Boy Jack]]''\n| Caroline Kipling\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[The Sunday Night Project]]''\n| Herself\n| Guest host; series 5, episode 13\n|-\n| 2009\u20132011\n| ''[[Producing Parker]]''\n| Dee (voice)\n| 26 episodes\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[Who Do You Think You Are? (UK TV series)|Who Do You Think You Are?]]'' (UK)\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Kim Cattrall\"\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''The Simpsons''\n| Fourth Simpsons child (voice)\n| Episode: \"[[O Brother, Where Bart Thou?]]\"\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Any Human Heart (miniseries)|Any Human Heart]]''\n| Gloria Scabius\n| Miniseries; 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Who Do You Think You Are? (U.S. TV series)|Who Do You Think You Are?]]'' (US)\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Kim Cattrall\"\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Red Nose Day 2011#Sketches and features|Upstairs Downstairs Abbey]]''\n| Countess of Grantham\n| [[Red Nose Day 2011]] telethon sketch\n|-\n| 2013\u20132016\n| ''[[Sensitive Skin (Canadian TV series)|Sensitive Skin]]''\n| Davina Jackson\n| Main role; 12 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[The Witness for the Prosecution (TV series)|The Witness for the Prosecution]]''\n| Emily French\n| Miniseries; 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Modus (TV series)|Modus]]''\n| US President Helen Tyler\n| Season 2\n|-\n| 2018\u20132019\n| ''[[Tell Me a Story (TV series)|Tell Me a Story]]''\n| Colleen Powell\n| Main role (Season 1)<ref>{{cite web|last1=Otterson|first1=Joe|title=Kim Cattrall to Star in CBS All Access Series 'Tell Me a Story'|url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/kim-cattrall-cbs-all-access-tell-me-a-story-1202819759/|website=Variety|accessdate=23 May 2018|date=23 May 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Filthy Rich (2020 TV series)|Filthy Rich]]''\n| Margaret Monreaux\n| Lead role\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n|-\n| 1982\n| [[3rd Genie Awards|Genie Award]